      <div class="txt">to any rating agency, insurer or insurance broker, or direct or indirect provider of credit protection to any Permitted Party, as required under Applicable Law or by a Governmental Authority.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">21.1.2.</div>
      <div class="txt">The Lender and/or any third party mentioned in this Clause may transfer and disclose any such information as required under Applicable Law or by any Governmental Authority or by an agreement between the Lender and any Governmental Authority.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">21.2.</div>
      <div class="txt"><b>Other Disclosures</b></div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">21.2.1.</div>
      <div class="txt">The Borrower agrees and confirms that as a pre-condition, to the grant of the Facility by the Lender to the Borrower, the Lender, requires consent of the Borrower to make certain disclosures in relation to the Borrower including information and data relating to the Borrower and any credit facility availed or to be availed by the Borrower, obligations assumed or to be assumed by the Borrower in relation thereto and default, if any, committed by the Borrower in discharge thereof. Accordingly, the Borrower hereby agrees and gives consent to the disclosure by the Lender of all or any such;</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">21.2.1.1.</div>
      <div class="txt">information and data relating to the Borrower;</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">21.2.1.2.</div>
      <div class="txt">the information or data relating to any credit facilities including, the Facility availed of or to be availed of by the Borrower from the Lender and the Borrower's obligations in any credit facility granted/to be granted, by the Lender (including the Facility); and</div>
