    <div class="section-heading">27. AMENDMENT</div>

    <p>No provision of this Agreement may be amended or waived except by written agreement between the Parties.</p>

    <div class="section-heading">28. REMEDIES AND WAIVERS; CONTINUING OBLIGATION</div>

    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">28.1.</div>
      <div class="txt">No failure to exercise, nor any delay in exercising, on the part of the Lender, any right or remedy under the Finance Documents will operate as a waiver, nor will any single or partial exercise of any right or remedy prevent any further or other exercise or the exercise of any other right or remedy. The rights and remedies provided in this Agreement and the other Finance Documents are cumulative and not exclusive of any rights or remedies provided by Applicable Law.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">28.2.</div>
      <div class="txt">The Borrower's obligations hereunder shall remain in full force and shall not be affected, impaired, diminished or extinguished by any act, omission, default, matter or thing (including anything which, but for this Clause, would have discharged the Borrower (wholly or in part) or would have afforded the Borrower any legal or equitable defense) except the full, prompt and complete performance of all the terms, undertakings and conditions of the Finance Documents, including the due and punctual payment of all amounts that may become due to the Lender under the Finance Documents.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-heading">29. MISCELLANEOUS</div>

    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">29.1.</div>
      <div class="txt">The Borrower confirms that it has received, read and understood the Key Fact Statement (KFS) and all material terms of the Loan Facility, including the rate of interest, charges, repayment schedule and Cooling-off Period, prior to execution of this Agreement.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">29.2.</div>
      <div class="txt">Any notice or communication under this Agreement shall be given in writing and shall be deemed to have been duly given if delivered by hand, courier, registered post or email to the address or contact details of the Parties as set out in Schedule 1 or as may be updated from time to time.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">29.3.</div>
      <div class="txt">The Borrower agrees that this Agreement and any related documents may be executed and communicated electronically, including through electronic signatures, and such execution shall be valid, binding and enforceable.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">29.4.</div>
      <div class="txt">This Agreement constitutes the entire agreement between the Parties with respect to the subject matter hereof and supersedes all prior discussions, representations or arrangements.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">29.5.</div>
      <div class="txt">The provisions relating to indemnity, confidentiality, payment obligations and any other provisions which by their nature are intended to survive shall survive termination or repayment of the Loan Facility.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <div class="num wide">29.6.</div>
      <div class="txt">The Lender shall not be liable for any failure or delay in performing its obligations under this Agreement if such failure or delay is due to events beyond its reasonable control.</div>
    </div>

